Apia, Savai'i, Samoa

Samoa Villas is a small individually owned group of Samoan style bungalows and villas with terraced lawns and tropical foliage. Located on the waterfront this property offers true peace and is a perfect place to go and relax by the pool and go and explore the island. There are five unit in all villas in the group so the place can take in family and group bookings too. There is a general licenced cafe where the leasing agent works and just next door is another bar and cafe.
